column1: Interest Rates of Outstanding Savings Bonds

*Where the issue date,coupon date or maturity date specified above falls on a day that the electronic payment system, established by the Monetary Authority of Singapore, is not in operation, issuance or redemption,

as the case may be, will be effected on the next business day when the electronic payment system is in operation. Business day means any day from Monday to Friday except a public or bank holiday in Singapore.
** At the end of each year, on a compounded basis.
